{"type": "article", "id": 11713, "title": "毛毡台灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-07T12:15:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000136ZS68Dx97rGvgn1Vl.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tMetrocuadro Design 是一家意大利设计工作室，他们试图“在裁缝店里面做家具”，于是在最近推出了一款全手工台灯，台灯外套整体由灰色毛毡制成，使用红色线和纽扣进行连接，白天台灯看上去干净利落，晚上暖洋洋的灯光会透过毛毡和缝隙洒在桌台上，看上去十分可爱。台灯售价 95 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.metrocuadro-design.com/products/2013-10-01-15-01-29/sleeve-lamp.html\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。这是<a href=\"http://www.metrocuadro-design.com/\" target=\"_blank\">工作室的官方主页</a>，风格简单有趣，感兴趣的话可以点击查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135754Rtd2hlDBOu9A8Mve.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135755XEF5M4qLdWVwKhS2.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135756K9zsQORmoVqbJYhD.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261357566xKaq78EJ0onjNrO.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135757Rw3JcsL9dkYlqIAp.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072613575862Z8XC9rx5dsKwn7.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135758vgQYBDcip0Kh2Esw.jpg\